cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper focuses on the application of event cameras in self-driving cars, which falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The use of deep neural networks for prediction tasks suggests that it could also belong to machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE) sub-categories.
